Saturday was absolutely beautiful thank you all so much for showing up! Can’t wait to do it again. Hope to see you there:) tickets are selling really well so grab one at Joeyharkum.com/tour if you’re planning on attending.

Playing a very special songwriter night this Saturday (12/17) in Berlin, MD at @globegastrotheatre with special guest @raywroten opening the night! If you’re in the area grab a ticket we would love to see you! Joeyharkum.com/tour for more info.

Practicing some old ones for this Saturday! So excited for this show. There’s still a few tickets left if you are in the area. @globegastrotheatre in Berlin, MD this Saturday 12/17. Doors at 7 music at 8. The delightful @raywroten will be opening the night. Tickets at Joeyharkum.com

D.C.! Very excited to announce that we will be rocking full band with our brothers @bumpinugliesmusic and @highereduband at the legendary @930club on May 4th! Grab a ticket at Joeyharkum.com/tour or in my bio!

Berlin, MD tomorrow night (12/17)! There’s only a few tickets left so grab em if you’re planning on coming! Can’t wait! Doors at 7PM @raywroten 8PM then a long set from me. Hope to see you! Tickets at Joeyharkum.com

Massive thank you to everyone who attended the Sold Out show at @globegastrotheatre on Saturday. It was so much fun to strip down the songs and talk about the meanings behind them. Great seeing so many friends and playing some songs with my brother @raywroten ❤️. A sold out acoustic show is a big deal and I’m grateful! 

📸 @nataleedehart

I can’t help myself I have to redo the van for every occasion. Pretty stoked on this new layout though. Got room for everyone to be comfy and in a seat belt with a full size bunk also for when the driver finishes his shift. Room in the back for personal bags and an inverter hooked up to the back battery for everyone’s computers. Gonna be a smooth ride! I had such a great time meeting up and hanging out with Joey Harkum, a powerhouse of a singer-songwriter from Pasadena, Maryland. I personally love Joey’s short and sweet lyrical style, with his hard hitting, super catchy tunes, its no surprise he has garnered the success he has.

Joey has been in this game for a decade, playing all throughout the country, heading and supporting big national acts. Catch Joey on tour this summer, including many shows with Tropidelic.
